{"word":"H4033 - מָגוּר - mâgûwr - maw-goor' - Dwelling","slug":"H4033","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָגוּר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mâgûwr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>maw-goor'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Dwelling"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D2;&#x05E8;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05D2;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05E8; - ma&#x0302;gu&#x0302;r  ma&#x0302;gu&#x0302;r</b> - <i>maw-goor', maw-goor'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H1481\">H1481</a> in the sense of <i>lodging</i>; a temporary <i>abode</i>; by extension a permanent <i>residence</i>: - dwelling, pilgrimage, where sojourn, be a stranger. Compare <a href=\"#/H4032\">H4032</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1481\">H1481</a>, <a href=\"#/H1483\">H1483</a>, <a href=\"#/H1485\">H1485</a>, <a href=\"#/H1616\">H1616</a>, <a href=\"#/H1628\">H1628</a>, <a href=\"#/H3017\">H3017</a>, <a href=\"#/H4035\">H4035</a>, <a href=\"#/H4460\">H4460</a>"}]}